[
  {
    "text": "This is real life firebending.",
    "start": 0.28,
    "duration": 1.813
  },
  {
    "text": "We're also testing the\nworld's strongest laser,",
    "start": 2.175,
    "duration": 2.847
  },
  {
    "text": "melting through metal with my finger\nand making a giant flaming rocket.",
    "start": 5.104,
    "duration": 4.343
  },
  {
    "text": "Starting with level one,\nwe're gonna make a mini rocket at home.",
    "start": 9.529,
    "duration": 3.873
  },
  {
    "text": "This is 99% rubbing alcohol.",
    "start": 13.484,
    "duration": 1.649
  },
  {
    "text": "Just a little bit.",
    "start": 15.215,
    "duration": 1.094
  },
  {
    "text": "You just want to coat the sides.",
    "start": 16.327,
    "duration": 3.338
  },
  {
    "text": "We drilled a hole in the\nmiddle of the bottle cap.",
    "start": 19.747,
    "duration": 5.162
  },
  {
    "text": "This might break some things, but",
    "start": 24.991,
    "duration": 3.42
  },
  {
    "text": "3, 2, 1.",
    "start": 28.431,
    "duration": 0.908
  },
  {
    "text": "My God, that's crazy.",
    "start": 29.421,
    "duration": 1.883
  },
  {
    "text": "And that was just level one.",
    "start": 31.724,
    "duration": 1.593
  },
  {
    "text": "Later in the video,",
    "start": 33.399,
    "duration": 1.045
  },
  {
    "text": "we're making a flaming rocket\nthat's gonna fly ten times higher,",
    "start": 34.526,
    "duration": 3.715
  },
  {
    "text": "a giant smoke cannon,\nand so much more.",
    "start": 38.323,
    "duration": 2.296
  },
  {
    "text": "I did not sign up for this.",
    "start": 40.637,
    "duration": 1.503
  },
  {
    "text": "Onto the next level.",
    "start": 42.252,
    "duration": 1.366
  },
  {
    "text": "This next experiment is\ncalled the fire tornado.",
    "start": 43.7,
    "duration": 3.295
  },
  {
    "text": "I need you to rip this sponge\ninto small little pieces and",
    "start": 47.077,
    "duration": 4.047
  },
  {
    "text": "put it in this container.",
    "start": 51.206,
    "duration": 1.698
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't need this no more.",
    "start": 52.986,
    "duration": 1.606
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, this is a can of butane, which is",
    "start": 54.674,
    "duration": 2.633
  },
  {
    "text": "lighter fluid.",
    "start": 57.427,
    "duration": 0.967
  },
  {
    "text": "Light it.",
    "start": 58.394,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "We're adding a fencing to allow\nair to flow in a circular motion.",
    "start": 61.224,
    "duration": 4.557
  },
  {
    "text": "And once we spin it, it creates.",
    "start": 65.863,
    "duration": 2.181
  },
  {
    "text": "A giant tornado effect,\ncreate a nice little tornado effect.",
    "start": 68.126,
    "duration": 4.203
  },
  {
    "text": "And if we put a balloon over it.",
    "start": 72.449,
    "duration": 2.235
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my God.",
    "start": 77.344,
    "duration": 1.128
  },
  {
    "text": "Onto the next experiment.",
    "start": 78.648,
    "duration": 1.503
  },
  {
    "text": "Next we have two aluminum can experiments.",
    "start": 80.151,
    "duration": 2.141
  },
  {
    "text": "For the first one,\nwe just need some drain cleaner,",
    "start": 82.374,
    "duration": 2.556
  },
  {
    "text": "stuff you can buy",
    "start": 84.93,
    "duration": 0.911
  },
  {
    "text": "At the hardware store.",
    "start": 85.923,
    "duration": 1.364
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm gonna fill this up now,\nas my assistant,",
    "start": 87.369,
    "duration": 2.847
  },
  {
    "text": "I need you to sand this coke can.",
    "start": 90.298,
    "duration": 2.156
  },
  {
    "text": "That's pretty good.",
    "start": 93.754,
    "duration": 1.225
  },
  {
    "text": "Now we've sanded off all the labels.",
    "start": 95.061,
    "duration": 2.359
  },
  {
    "text": "Ooh.",
    "start": 97.94,
    "duration": 0.333
  },
  {
    "text": "We're gonna put this in...",
    "start": 98.355,
    "duration": 1.7
  },
  {
    "text": "instantly dissolving.",
    "start": 100.137,
    "duration": 1.357
  },
  {
    "text": "That's crazy.",
    "start": 101.494,
    "duration": 0.995
  },
  {
    "text": "Up next is aluminum can versus gallium.",
    "start": 102.535,
    "duration": 2.189
  },
  {
    "text": "So the special thing about gallium is\nthe fact that when it comes in",
    "start": 104.806,
    "duration": 3.901
  },
  {
    "text": "contact with any aluminum surface,",
    "start": 108.789,
    "duration": 1.91
  },
  {
    "text": "it will melt the aluminum.",
    "start": 110.781,
    "duration": 1.441
  },
  {
    "text": "We can put the gallium on top.",
    "start": 112.304,
    "duration": 1.648
  },
  {
    "text": "Why don't you spread it around?..",
    "start": 114.034,
    "duration": 1.831
  },
  {
    "text": "Safety touch.",
    "start": 115.865,
    "duration": 0.754
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll need some time for the\nmelting process to happen,",
    "start": 116.701,
    "duration": 3.131
  },
  {
    "text": "so we'll check back on both aluminum\ncan experiments later in the video.",
    "start": 119.914,
    "duration": 4.166
  },
  {
    "text": "This next experiment needs\nto be done in the car.",
    "start": 124.192,
    "duration": 2.769
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll just start with some Elmer's glue.",
    "start": 127.043,
    "duration": 2.276
  },
  {
    "text": "You're pouring glue in the car?",
    "start": 129.337,
    "duration": 1.288
  },
  {
    "text": "Hafu.",
    "start": 130.625,
    "duration": 0.214
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you sure you're going\nto be able to get that out?",
    "start": 130.921,
    "duration": 2.231
  },
  {
    "text": "We gotta trust science.",
    "start": 133.248,
    "duration": 1.359
  },
  {
    "text": "Pour this into the cup.",
    "start": 134.689,
    "duration": 1.317
  },
  {
    "text": "Shake it up.",
    "start": 136.006,
    "duration": 0.781
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's hope this works.",
    "start": 136.869,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "What if it goes into the",
    "start": 138.163,
    "duration": 1.864
  },
  {
    "text": "engine?",
    "start": 140.467,
    "duration": 0.702
  },
  {
    "text": "Into the engine?",
    "start": 141.251,
    "duration": 1.243
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, we have our beautiful slime.",
    "start": 144.394,
    "duration": 3.188
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, this should clean our car...",
    "start": 147.664,
    "duration": 2.65
  },
  {
    "text": "Clean the cup holder.",
    "start": 150.396,
    "duration": 1.698
  },
  {
    "text": "Clean up some dust here.",
    "start": 153.274,
    "duration": 1.603
  },
  {
    "text": "Clean up some dust.",
    "start": 154.997,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's clean the steering wheel...",
    "start": 156.347,
    "duration": 2.467
  },
  {
    "text": "Look at that.",
    "start": 158.814,
    "duration": 0.895
  },
  {
    "text": "It's sucking everything up.",
    "start": 159.791,
    "duration": 1.81
  },
  {
    "text": "That's so, so gross.",
    "start": 161.651,
    "duration": 1.547
  },
  {
    "text": "Now we have a brand new car.",
    "start": 163.366,
    "duration": 1.429
  },
  {
    "text": "Completely cleaned with glue.",
    "start": 164.877,
    "duration": 1.488
  },
  {
    "text": "This next experiment is\na carbon sugar snake.",
    "start": 166.399,
    "duration": 2.734
  },
  {
    "text": "This is our snake right here.",
    "start": 169.215,
    "duration": 1.702
  },
  {
    "text": "It's just a mix of baking soda and sugar.",
    "start": 170.999,
    "duration": 2.44
  },
  {
    "text": "What I need you to do is\npour the rubbing alcohol.",
    "start": 173.521,
    "duration": 2.993
  },
  {
    "text": "We want to pour this very concentrated.",
    "start": 176.596,
    "duration": 2.358
  },
  {
    "text": "Ready?",
    "start": 179.954,
    "duration": 0.697
  },
  {
    "text": "One, two, three.",
    "start": 180.733,
    "duration": 1.331
  },
  {
    "text": "Carbon sugar snake come alive.",
    "start": 182.146,
    "duration": 2.608
  },
  {
    "text": "So the sugar and the baking soda\nis now reacting with the fire.",
    "start": 186.774,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "As the mixture burns, the carbon dioxide",
    "start": 190.894,
    "duration": 2.455
  },
  {
    "text": "Gas is getting trapped inside, which is",
    "start": 193.367,
    "duration": 2.342
  },
  {
    "text": "Making the sugar come alive.",
    "start": 195.727,
    "duration": 2.223
  },
  {
    "text": "What are you gonna name your monster?",
    "start": 198.062,
    "duration": 1.714
  },
  {
    "text": "Hafu?",
    "start": 199.776,
    "duration": 0.317
  },
  {
    "text": "Big Willy?",
    "start": 200.093,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm sorry, my man.",
    "start": 201.891,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "Cool thing about this,",
    "start": 205.574,
    "duration": 1.156
  },
  {
    "text": "you can actually touch it after\nit feels like a croissant.",
    "start": 206.812,
    "duration": 3.074
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah",
    "start": 209.886,
    "duration": 0.218
  },
  {
    "text": "you can,\nlike,",
    "start": 210.104,
    "duration": 0.796
  },
  {
    "text": "peel it open,\nspread it open.",
    "start": 210.982,
    "duration": 1.569
  },
  {
    "text": "We basically made bread.",
    "start": 212.633,
    "duration": 1.253
  },
  {
    "text": "Alright, on to the next experiment.",
    "start": 213.968,
    "duration": 1.864
  },
  {
    "text": "This next experiment only\ninvolves a simple egg.",
    "start": 215.914,
    "duration": 2.596
  },
  {
    "text": "This is what happens when you drop an egg",
    "start": 218.592,
    "duration": 2.253
  },
  {
    "text": "Normally",
    "start": 220.845,
    "duration": 0.661
  },
  {
    "text": "it breaks as expected.",
    "start": 221.588,
    "duration": 1.423
  },
  {
    "text": "But when you put an egg and\nsoak it in vinegar for two days,",
    "start": 223.093,
    "duration": 4.073
  },
  {
    "text": "this is what happens.",
    "start": 227.248,
    "duration": 1.373
  },
  {
    "text": "Our egg is now see through.",
    "start": 228.703,
    "duration": 1.765
  },
  {
    "text": "And what happened here is the acid in\nthe vinegar has actually broken down",
    "start": 230.55,
    "duration": 5.056
  },
  {
    "text": "the hard part of the egg shell,",
    "start": 235.688,
    "duration": 2.071
  },
  {
    "text": "which became these bubbles.",
    "start": 237.841,
    "duration": 1.793
  },
  {
    "text": "This is a before, and this is the after.",
    "start": 239.716,
    "duration": 2.668
  },
  {
    "text": "Now,\nwhat's left intact is a membrane inside,",
    "start": 242.466,
    "duration": 3.068
  },
  {
    "text": "so the egg",
    "start": 245.534,
    "duration": 0.82
  },
  {
    "text": "is actually bouncing.",
    "start": 246.436,
    "duration": 1.388
  },
  {
    "text": "Look at this.",
    "start": 248.76,
    "duration": 0.993
  },
  {
    "text": "That's so cool.",
    "start": 249.753,
    "duration": 0.976
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's make a bet.",
    "start": 250.794,
    "duration": 0.983
  },
  {
    "text": "Loser.",
    "start": 251.777,
    "duration": 0.369
  },
  {
    "text": "How's you eat this?",
    "start": 252.228,
    "duration": 1.13
  },
  {
    "text": "Make a bet on how high you think\nthis egg can bounce without breaking.",
    "start": 253.468,
    "duration": 4.127
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm gonna say",
    "start": 257.595,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "here.",
    "start": 258.395,
    "duration": 0.785
  },
  {
    "text": "You're gonna say higher than me...",
    "start": 259.994,
    "duration": 2.016
  },
  {
    "text": "Then I'm gonna say here.",
    "start": 262.092,
    "duration": 1.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, ready?",
    "start": 263.462,
    "duration": 0.876
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll go here.",
    "start": 264.338,
    "duration": 0.864
  },
  {
    "text": "First.",
    "start": 265.202,
    "duration": 0.862
  },
  {
    "text": "You're eating the egg.",
    "start": 269.354,
    "duration": 1.378
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm closer.",
    "start": 270.732,
    "duration": 0.805
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, that's disgusting.",
    "start": 271.619,
    "duration": 1.196
  },
  {
    "text": "That is actually disgusting.",
    "start": 272.897,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "You're eating the egg.",
    "start": 274.523,
    "duration": 1.451
  },
  {
    "text": "Honestly, it just tastes like pickles.",
    "start": 282.204,
    "duration": 2.356
  },
  {
    "text": "Pretty cool science experiment.",
    "start": 284.642,
    "duration": 1.873
  },
  {
    "text": "Very easy to do.",
    "start": 286.565,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "Next,\nthis is a normal lighter,",
    "start": 287.606,
    "duration": 1.876
  },
  {
    "text": "but we're gonna turn it\ninto a magic lighter.",
    "start": 289.564,
    "duration": 2.76
  },
  {
    "text": "All right.",
    "start": 292.324,
    "duration": 0.671
  },
  {
    "text": "What does that mean?",
    "start": 293.077,
    "duration": 1.063
  },
  {
    "text": "We need the lights off...",
    "start": 294.332,
    "duration": 1.762
  },
  {
    "text": "So what I'm gonna need\nyou to do is just blow",
    "start": 296.176,
    "duration": 3.206
  },
  {
    "text": "harder.",
    "start": 299.942,
    "duration": 0.583
  },
  {
    "text": "Blow harder.",
    "start": 300.525,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Did you see that?",
    "start": 307.432,
    "duration": 1.072
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, that was really cool.",
    "start": 308.624,
    "duration": 1.496
  },
  {
    "text": "So when the flame blows out,",
    "start": 310.232,
    "duration": 1.452
  },
  {
    "text": "there's actually leftover\nwax in the smoke.",
    "start": 311.766,
    "duration": 2.21
  },
  {
    "text": "That's why when you add heat,\nit will relight on fire.",
    "start": 314.058,
    "duration": 2.798
  },
  {
    "text": "This next experiment\nis called fire suction.",
    "start": 316.96,
    "duration": 2.326
  },
  {
    "text": "So I'm gonna need your help later.",
    "start": 319.368,
    "duration": 1.77
  },
  {
    "text": "First,\nwe're just gonna light this candle,",
    "start": 321.22,
    "duration": 2.235
  },
  {
    "text": "pour a little bit of water around.",
    "start": 323.537,
    "duration": 1.794
  },
  {
    "text": "I said a little bit.",
    "start": 325.413,
    "duration": 1.008
  },
  {
    "text": "Place this on top,\nplace a glass over it,",
    "start": 326.503,
    "duration": 2.174
  },
  {
    "text": "which is gonna create a\nsuction once the fire dies out.",
    "start": 328.759,
    "duration": 2.944
  },
  {
    "text": "And while we wait for the fire to die out,",
    "start": 331.785,
    "duration": 2.231
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to solve this\nRubik's cube so we can test",
    "start": 334.098,
    "duration": 2.765
  },
  {
    "text": "The strength of this suction.",
    "start": 336.905,
    "duration": 1.619
  },
  {
    "text": "Ooh, yeah, it's working.",
    "start": 341.904,
    "duration": 1.975
  },
  {
    "text": "Nice!",
    "start": 343.879,
    "duration": 0.347
  },
  {
    "text": "Place a Rubik's cube on top",
    "start": 344.308,
    "duration": 1.832
  },
  {
    "text": "One, two, three.",
    "start": 347.2,
    "duration": 1.794
  },
  {
    "text": "Last one.",
    "start": 349.114,
    "duration": 1.024
  },
  {
    "text": "Hurry up.",
    "start": 350.22,
    "duration": 1.024
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, there we go.",
    "start": 351.584,
    "duration": 1.287
  },
  {
    "text": "What else can we place on top?",
    "start": 352.953,
    "duration": 1.697
  },
  {
    "text": "Can we place this perfume can on top?",
    "start": 354.732,
    "duration": 2.111
  },
  {
    "text": "Can we place this goggle on top?",
    "start": 356.925,
    "duration": 1.815
  },
  {
    "text": "Can we place.",
    "start": 358.74,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, okay.",
    "start": 359.689,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "Now we can weigh out",
    "start": 361.184,
    "duration": 1.625
  },
  {
    "text": "everything on top,\nand that's a total of 1161 grams.",
    "start": 362.929,
    "duration": 4.23
  },
  {
    "text": "The power of this tiny little candle.",
    "start": 367.241,
    "duration": 2.958
  },
  {
    "text": "Next experiment.",
    "start": 370.263,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "This next experiment is\ncalled water suction.",
    "start": 371.383,
    "duration": 2.894
  },
  {
    "text": "Should I be concerned?",
    "start": 374.303,
    "duration": 1.279
  },
  {
    "text": "Just a little.",
    "start": 375.618,
    "duration": 0.899
  },
  {
    "text": "You're gonna put some food covering\nin this water just so it's visible.",
    "start": 376.599,
    "duration": 4.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Swirl around.",
    "start": 380.779,
    "duration": 1.03
  },
  {
    "text": "And now we're gonna make me\nten times more attractive.",
    "start": 381.82,
    "duration": 3.225
  },
  {
    "text": "This is axe body spray.",
    "start": 385.127,
    "duration": 1.296
  },
  {
    "text": "Every high school man's dream.",
    "start": 386.505,
    "duration": 1.757
  },
  {
    "text": "Spray me.",
    "start": 388.3,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "How does it smell?",
    "start": 390.324,
    "duration": 1.331
  },
  {
    "text": "On the can of axe body spray,\nit has a fire emoji.",
    "start": 392.445,
    "duration": 3.699
  },
  {
    "text": "Woah that's cool",
    "start": 398.45,
    "duration": 1.393
  },
  {
    "text": "Kind of like a flamethrower.",
    "start": 399.925,
    "duration": 1.578
  },
  {
    "text": "But that's not our trick.",
    "start": 401.585,
    "duration": 1.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Our trick is we're gonna use this\ninside of the bottle just a little bit.",
    "start": 403.067,
    "duration": 4.246
  },
  {
    "text": "All this water will instantly\ngo into the bottle once.",
    "start": 407.395,
    "duration": 3.117
  },
  {
    "text": "I like this.",
    "start": 410.512,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa.",
    "start": 412.724,
    "duration": 0.67
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's water suction.",
    "start": 418.224,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Is fire suction cooler or water suction?",
    "start": 419.806,
    "duration": 2.383
  },
  {
    "text": "Water suction",
    "start": 422.25,
    "duration": 0.282
  },
  {
    "text": "When we're sucking,",
    "start": 423.191,
    "duration": 0.635
  },
  {
    "text": "it needs to be a little\nwet for it to be fun",
    "start": 423.908,
    "duration": 2.954
  },
  {
    "text": "right?",
    "start": 426.882,
    "duration": 0.621
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 427.503,
    "duration": 0.361
  },
  {
    "text": "Especially when it's red.",
    "start": 427.946,
    "duration": 1.766
  },
  {
    "text": "Next experiment.",
    "start": 429.888,
    "duration": 1.224
  },
  {
    "text": "So now we're gonna make\na dry ice bubble maker.",
    "start": 431.248,
    "duration": 2.92
  },
  {
    "text": "When we put dry ice in water",
    "start": 434.788,
    "duration": 1.739
  },
  {
    "text": ", it starts a reaction.",
    "start": 437.107,
    "duration": 1.429
  },
  {
    "text": "Look at that.",
    "start": 438.54,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "That looks pretty cool.",
    "start": 439.444,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "We're gonna now screw on the cap",
    "start": 440.544,
    "duration": 2.065
  },
  {
    "text": "and then",
    "start": 442.629,
    "duration": 0.695
  },
  {
    "text": "stick the tube in.",
    "start": 443.406,
    "duration": 1.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Not too far, though, just a little bit.",
    "start": 444.588,
    "duration": 2.479
  },
  {
    "text": "And",
    "start": 447.067,
    "duration": 0.423
  },
  {
    "text": "we'll just tape it.",
    "start": 447.572,
    "duration": 1.881
  },
  {
    "text": "Look at that dry ice bubble.",
    "start": 450.433,
    "duration": 2.831
  },
  {
    "text": "It's bouncing.",
    "start": 456.484,
    "duration": 1.039
  },
  {
    "text": "We're dipping the tube\ninto a dish soap solution.",
    "start": 457.525,
    "duration": 2.358
  },
  {
    "text": "The dry ice smoke gets\ntrapped in the dish soap,",
    "start": 459.885,
    "duration": 2.861
  },
  {
    "text": "which starts to form a bubble.",
    "start": 462.828,
    "duration": 1.707
  },
  {
    "text": "And our goal is to",
    "start": 464.617,
    "duration": 1.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Make the biggest bubble we can.",
    "start": 465.677,
    "duration": 1.606
  },
  {
    "text": "Trust the process.",
    "start": 467.283,
    "duration": 0.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Look how big this is.",
    "start": 467.885,
    "duration": 1.099
  },
  {
    "text": "Look how big of this is.",
    "start": 469.066,
    "duration": 1.308
  },
  {
    "text": "Next we have a chemistry experiment.",
    "start": 472.394,
    "duration": 1.909
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to show you how to make\nelephant toothpaste with just",
    "start": 474.385,
    "duration": 3.368
  },
  {
    "text": "grocery store ingredients.",
    "start": 477.835,
    "duration": 1.341
  },
  {
    "text": "All you need is some yeast,\nhydrogen peroxide,",
    "start": 479.258,
    "duration": 2.449
  },
  {
    "text": "which is for wounds,\nan empty bottle,",
    "start": 481.789,
    "duration": 1.953
  },
  {
    "text": "dish soap,\nand food coloring of your choice.",
    "start": 483.824,
    "duration": 2.338
  },
  {
    "text": "So first,",
    "start": 486.162,
    "duration": 0.497
  },
  {
    "text": "we just pour the hydrogen\nperoxide in here.",
    "start": 486.741,
    "duration": 2.291
  },
  {
    "text": "Talking about chemistry,\ndating seasoning is actually coming up,",
    "start": 489.114,
    "duration": 3.412
  },
  {
    "text": "so if you're still single,\nnow is the time to form a bond.",
    "start": 492.608,
    "duration": 3.085
  },
  {
    "text": "No more crying yourself to sleep\nat night or binging shows alone.",
    "start": 495.775,
    "duration": 3.518
  },
  {
    "text": "Our sponsor,\ncoffee meets bagel,",
    "start": 499.295,
    "duration": 2.103
  },
  {
    "text": "is here to help.",
    "start": 501.48,
    "duration": 0.97
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's add a little bit of dish soap.",
    "start": 502.532,
    "duration": 2.278
  },
  {
    "text": "and I'm going to add a",
    "start": 506.054,
    "duration": 1.127
  },
  {
    "text": "dash of red food coloring to signify love.",
    "start": 507.231,
    "duration": 2.512
  },
  {
    "text": "So coffee meets bagel is the\nlast dating app you'll ever need.",
    "start": 509.825,
    "duration": 3.7
  },
  {
    "text": "It's made for those only looking\nfor serious relationships.",
    "start": 513.607,
    "duration": 3.517
  },
  {
    "text": "If you download the app and you say\nyou're looking for something casual,",
    "start": 517.206,
    "duration": 4.344
  },
  {
    "text": "they'll actually redirect you\nto competitor dating apps.",
    "start": 521.632,
    "duration": 3.361
  },
  {
    "text": "Im a very career focused person and\nim sure a lot of you are just like me.",
    "start": 525.075,
    "duration": 4.432
  },
  {
    "text": "So swiping through profiles might\nseem like a waste of time for you.",
    "start": 529.589,
    "duration": 4.13
  },
  {
    "text": "Thats why I love coffee meets bagels.",
    "start": 533.737,
    "duration": 2.074
  },
  {
    "text": "Matching feature.",
    "start": 535.814,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "Instead of endlessly swiping,",
    "start": 536.855,
    "duration": 1.576
  },
  {
    "text": "you get suggested new matches\nbased on your dating preferences.",
    "start": 538.513,
    "duration": 3.519
  },
  {
    "text": "For example,",
    "start": 542.032,
    "duration": 0.689
  },
  {
    "text": "you can say you like girls\nwho work out and don't party.",
    "start": 542.803,
    "duration": 3.132
  },
  {
    "text": "Also they have an icebreaker\nfeature which makes it a little",
    "start": 546.017,
    "duration": 3.33
  },
  {
    "text": "less awkward for you to slide in.",
    "start": 549.429,
    "duration": 1.794
  },
  {
    "text": "No more hey double y.",
    "start": 551.305,
    "duration": 1.141
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's continue.",
    "start": 552.616,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "We have our yeasat.",
    "start": 553.602,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's add it to some warm water.",
    "start": 554.643,
    "duration": 1.579
  },
  {
    "text": "The yeast would be the catalyst that\nwill start this chemical reaction.",
    "start": 556.304,
    "duration": 3.604
  },
  {
    "text": "One of my friends from university\nactually found his girlfriend",
    "start": 559.99,
    "duration": 3.226
  },
  {
    "text": "using coffee meats bagel.",
    "start": 563.298,
    "duration": 1.231
  },
  {
    "text": "And from talking to all my\nfriends that use the app,",
    "start": 564.611,
    "duration": 2.655
  },
  {
    "text": "they vouch that the people on\ncoffee meets bagel are a lot more",
    "start": 567.348,
    "duration": 3.234
  },
  {
    "text": "wholesome than the other apps.",
    "start": 570.664,
    "duration": 1.553
  },
  {
    "text": "Now,\nthis is the last step to our experiment.",
    "start": 572.243,
    "duration": 2.478
  },
  {
    "text": "We add the catalyst into\nthe solution that we made.",
    "start": 574.803,
    "duration": 2.756
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're single and looking\nfor a serious relationship,",
    "start": 577.641,
    "duration": 3.079
  },
  {
    "text": "download coffee meets bagel for free\nusing the link in the description,",
    "start": 580.802,
    "duration": 3.925
  },
  {
    "text": "and get ready",
    "start": 584.727,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "to start a chemical reaction of love.",
    "start": 585.543,
    "duration": 2.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa.",
    "start": 592.604,
    "duration": 0.71
  },
  {
    "text": "Hopefully you don't explode\nthis fast on your first date.",
    "start": 599.604,
    "duration": 2.941
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, it's been over an hour.",
    "start": 602.627,
    "duration": 1.697
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's check back on our\naluminum can experiments.",
    "start": 604.406,
    "duration": 2.481
  },
  {
    "text": "Got the drain cleaner one right here.",
    "start": 606.969,
    "duration": 1.854
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's pull this one first.",
    "start": 608.905,
    "duration": 1.319
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh,",
    "start": 612.764,
    "duration": 0.851
  },
  {
    "text": "look at that.",
    "start": 613.865,
    "duration": 1.31
  },
  {
    "text": "It's smoking.",
    "start": 615.175,
    "duration": 0.855
  },
  {
    "text": "So the drain cleaner has\nmelted away all the aluminum,",
    "start": 616.112,
    "duration": 3.5
  },
  {
    "text": "and the only thing that's\nleft is a plastic wrap inside.",
    "start": 619.694,
    "duration": 3.633
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a spongy can.",
    "start": 623.409,
    "duration": 1.143
  },
  {
    "text": "That's so cool.",
    "start": 624.644,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "This is a gallium can.",
    "start": 628.904,
    "duration": 1.141
  },
  {
    "text": "We left it there for a couple hours.",
    "start": 630.127,
    "duration": 1.853
  },
  {
    "text": "I noticed some interesting textures.",
    "start": 632.062,
    "duration": 1.852
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's see what happens.",
    "start": 633.996,
    "duration": 1.154
  },
  {
    "text": "So,\nas you can see,",
    "start": 635.232,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "this can has become destroyed.",
    "start": 636.274,
    "duration": 1.563
  },
  {
    "text": "Give it a little squish test.",
    "start": 637.919,
    "duration": 1.481
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's try poking through with our fingers.",
    "start": 640.984,
    "duration": 2.62
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my God.",
    "start": 646.672,
    "duration": 1.172
  },
  {
    "text": "We can basically crumple this can.",
    "start": 648.744,
    "duration": 2.433
  },
  {
    "text": "It's like an aluminum croissant.",
    "start": 651.259,
    "duration": 2.287
  },
  {
    "text": "Next we have two tiny air guns.",
    "start": 653.666,
    "duration": 2.229
  },
  {
    "text": "So how this works, it's literally just",
    "start": 655.929,
    "duration": 1.47
  },
  {
    "text": "A cup and a balloon\nattached to the back end.",
    "start": 657.457,
    "duration": 2.499
  },
  {
    "text": "You feel that?",
    "start": 659.956,
    "duration": 0.795
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah",
    "start": 660.751,
    "duration": 0.544
  },
  {
    "text": "To see if it actually is working,",
    "start": 661.377,
    "duration": 1.9
  },
  {
    "text": "let's light it on fire.",
    "start": 663.397,
    "duration": 1.353
  },
  {
    "text": "Why does every experiment\ninvolve fire here?",
    "start": 664.862,
    "duration": 2.623
  },
  {
    "text": "Cause fire is cool.",
    "start": 667.519,
    "duration": 1.423
  },
  {
    "text": "Try blowing this out.",
    "start": 669.038,
    "duration": 1.156
  },
  {
    "text": "There we go.",
    "start": 671.234,
    "duration": 0.895
  },
  {
    "text": "That's pretty cool, right?",
    "start": 672.211,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah",
    "start": 673.679,
    "duration": 0.71
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's step it up a little bit.",
    "start": 674.471,
    "duration": 1.83
  },
  {
    "text": "That's huge.",
    "start": 676.301,
    "duration": 0.546
  },
  {
    "text": "What are we blowing with that?",
    "start": 676.929,
    "duration": 1.364
  },
  {
    "text": "Your mom?",
    "start": 678.293,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "So what we can do is actually,\nwe can just burn a little paper,",
    "start": 679.015,
    "duration": 3.636
  },
  {
    "text": "and it will become a smoke cannon.",
    "start": 682.733,
    "duration": 1.925
  },
  {
    "text": "Can just put the paper inside.",
    "start": 684.74,
    "duration": 1.671
  },
  {
    "text": "Our smoke cannon is now loaded with smoke.",
    "start": 686.493,
    "duration": 2.412
  },
  {
    "text": "We can aim and fire it.",
    "start": 688.987,
    "duration": 1.285
  },
  {
    "text": "So we got bottles set up over there.",
    "start": 690.354,
    "duration": 2.056
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's the challenge.",
    "start": 692.492,
    "duration": 1.213
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoever knocks down the\nmost number of bottles wins,",
    "start": 693.739,
    "duration": 2.926
  },
  {
    "text": "and the loser has to drink lemon juice.",
    "start": 696.747,
    "duration": 2.137
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay,",
    "start": 698.884,
    "duration": 0.287
  },
  {
    "text": "we get three shots each.",
    "start": 699.253,
    "duration": 1.349
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay?",
    "start": 700.602,
    "duration": 0.298
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, I'll go first.",
    "start": 700.982,
    "duration": 1.152
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, you see that?",
    "start": 704.314,
    "duration": 0.979
  },
  {
    "text": "Need to aim it a little lower.",
    "start": 705.375,
    "duration": 1.759
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's see if you can beat that.",
    "start": 713.954,
    "duration": 1.62
  },
  {
    "text": "There we go.",
    "start": 716.454,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my gosh.",
    "start": 720.334,
    "duration": 0.923
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on.",
    "start": 721.257,
    "duration": 0.696
  },
  {
    "text": "Got one last shot.",
    "start": 722.035,
    "duration": 1.103
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my goodness.",
    "start": 723.266,
    "duration": 1.743
  },
  {
    "text": "We did it!",
    "start": 725.009,
    "duration": 0.944
  },
  {
    "text": "Shoot me, shoot me.",
    "start": 726.035,
    "duration": 1.459
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa.",
    "start": 728.174,
    "duration": 0.809
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa.",
    "start": 728.983,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Loser has to drink lemonade.",
    "start": 730.994,
    "duration": 1.904
  },
  {
    "text": "This is lemon juice.",
    "start": 733.066,
    "duration": 1.363
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not lemonade.",
    "start": 734.511,
    "duration": 1.223
  },
  {
    "text": "This is so sour.",
    "start": 740.234,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "Holy crap.",
    "start": 742.26,
    "duration": 0.919
  },
  {
    "text": "So this is the world's most\npowerful laser pointer.",
    "start": 743.261,
    "duration": 3.096
  },
  {
    "text": "We need a different type of\neye protection for this one.",
    "start": 746.439,
    "duration": 3.408
  },
  {
    "text": "We need",
    "start": 749.847,
    "duration": 0.556
  },
  {
    "text": "sunglasses.",
    "start": 750.403,
    "duration": 0.681
  },
  {
    "text": "Mine are actually red because it cancels\nout the blue light from the laser.",
    "start": 751.166,
    "duration": 4.621
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's test it on a balloon.",
    "start": 755.813,
    "duration": 1.651
  },
  {
    "text": "How many balloons do you think\nthis laser will burn through?",
    "start": 763.044,
    "duration": 2.927
  },
  {
    "text": "Three",
    "start": 766.053,
    "duration": 0.986
  },
  {
    "text": "Three?",
    "start": 767.039,
    "duration": 0.708
  },
  {
    "text": "I think it will burn\nthrough all these balloons.",
    "start": 767.829,
    "duration": 2.235
  },
  {
    "text": "So I've even set up a match at the end\nto see if I can light that on fire.",
    "start": 770.146,
    "duration": 3.49
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, ready?",
    "start": 773.636,
    "duration": 0.643
  },
  {
    "text": "Yep.",
    "start": 774.279,
    "duration": 0.507
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's see it.",
    "start": 774.868,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, that was fast.",
    "start": 777.064,
    "duration": 2.432
  },
  {
    "text": "3, 4, 5.",
    "start": 780.196,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "It kept going.",
    "start": 781.318,
    "duration": 1.147
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my God.",
    "start": 782.465,
    "duration": 0.95
  },
  {
    "text": "Six, seven",
    "start": 783.497,
    "duration": 3.126
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me go a little closer.",
    "start": 786.705,
    "duration": 1.459
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh,",
    "start": 790.484,
    "duration": 0.872
  },
  {
    "text": "this laser is cool.",
    "start": 791.926,
    "duration": 2.042
  },
  {
    "text": "And it was only, like, $70.",
    "start": 794.096,
    "duration": 1.369
  },
  {
    "text": "Only?",
    "start": 795.5,
    "duration": 0.128
  },
  {
    "text": "this next experiment only\nrequires hand sanitizer.",
    "start": 796.401,
    "duration": 1.762
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm sure you have some leftover,\nbut don't try this at home.",
    "start": 798.245,
    "duration": 2.96
  },
  {
    "text": "It's extremely dangerous.",
    "start": 801.287,
    "duration": 1.185
  },
  {
    "text": "It's called fire hand.",
    "start": 802.554,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "And in order for you to see this,\nwe need to turn the lights off.",
    "start": 803.67,
    "duration": 3.254
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, that's better.",
    "start": 807.192,
    "duration": 1.015
  },
  {
    "text": "First, we're gonna squeeze",
    "start": 808.233,
    "duration": 1.867
  },
  {
    "text": "the hand sanitizer onto our surface here,\nspread it around,",
    "start": 810.22,
    "duration": 4.235
  },
  {
    "text": "and then wet our hands so\nwe don't burn ourselves.",
    "start": 814.537,
    "duration": 3.542
  },
  {
    "text": "And then",
    "start": 818.079,
    "duration": 0.694
  },
  {
    "text": "last step.",
    "start": 818.773,
    "duration": 0.725
  },
  {
    "text": "A little bit more of hand\nsanitizer on our hand.",
    "start": 819.58,
    "duration": 3.459
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's watch the magic happen.",
    "start": 823.057,
    "duration": 2.027
  },
  {
    "text": "On to the next experiment.",
    "start": 835.884,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "All right,\nnow it's time for the final experiment.",
    "start": 837.486,
    "duration": 2.921
  },
  {
    "text": "We're gonna use everything we learned\nand combine it into a butane rocket.",
    "start": 840.489,
    "duration": 4.418
  },
  {
    "text": "What does that even mean?",
    "start": 844.933,
    "duration": 1.143
  },
  {
    "text": "Butane rocket.",
    "start": 846.211,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "So,\nbutane,",
    "start": 847.17,
    "duration": 0.789
  },
  {
    "text": "when it's combined with coke,\nit will react at such a fast",
    "start": 848.041,
    "duration": 4.122
  },
  {
    "text": "Pace that it becomes rocket fuel.",
    "start": 852.205,
    "duration": 1.686
  },
  {
    "text": "As my assistant, I need you to hold this.",
    "start": 853.941,
    "duration": 2.182
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait, let me think about this.",
    "start": 856.205,
    "duration": 1.752
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't want to blow you up.",
    "start": 858.039,
    "duration": 1.631
  },
  {
    "text": "So what I'm doing is I'm just letting\nthe butane out into the coke bottle.",
    "start": 859.752,
    "duration": 4.443
  },
  {
    "text": "We now have butane",
    "start": 864.277,
    "duration": 1.06
  },
  {
    "text": "in this container.",
    "start": 865.457,
    "duration": 1.065
  },
  {
    "text": "It is kind of smoking outside,\nas you can see.",
    "start": 866.604,
    "duration": 2.777
  },
  {
    "text": "Can you see that?",
    "start": 869.381,
    "duration": 0.91
  },
  {
    "text": "We're going to see how this goes.",
    "start": 870.373,
    "duration": 1.684
  },
  {
    "text": "One, two, three.",
    "start": 872.057,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay,\nwe didn't have enough butane in there.",
    "start": 874.374,
    "duration": 2.082
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay,\nso what we're going to do instead,",
    "start": 876.538,
    "duration": 1.873
  },
  {
    "text": "we're first going to fill up this\ncoke bottle with only butane,",
    "start": 878.493,
    "duration": 2.996
  },
  {
    "text": "and then we're going to pour\nit into this coke bottle.",
    "start": 881.571,
    "duration": 2.557
  },
  {
    "text": "On top,\nwe got a butane layer,",
    "start": 884.21,
    "duration": 1.385
  },
  {
    "text": "and then on the bottom,\nwe got a coke layer.",
    "start": 885.677,
    "duration": 2.07
  },
  {
    "text": "Once I flip this over,\nthat's when the reaction will start.",
    "start": 887.829,
    "duration": 2.764
  },
  {
    "text": "Butane rocket.",
    "start": 890.593,
    "duration": 0.748
  },
  {
    "text": "One, two, three.",
    "start": 891.423,
    "duration": 1.371
  },
  {
    "text": "Now we gotta do a bigger version of that,\nand on fire.",
    "start": 901.974,
    "duration": 3.093
  },
  {
    "text": "On fire?",
    "start": 905.55,
    "duration": 0.929
  },
  {
    "text": "We only have one shot for this,\nwe used three cans of butane,",
    "start": 906.561,
    "duration": 3.065
  },
  {
    "text": "and this is a big coke bottle.",
    "start": 909.708,
    "duration": 1.466
  },
  {
    "text": "And, guys, again, do not try this at home.",
    "start": 911.256,
    "duration": 2.062
  },
  {
    "text": "Now the butane is going\ninside the coke bottle.",
    "start": 913.4,
    "duration": 2.316
  },
  {
    "text": "I need you to step back.",
    "start": 915.798,
    "duration": 1.199
  },
  {
    "text": "You're gonna light this on fire.",
    "start": 917.023,
    "duration": 1.434
  },
  {
    "text": "You ready?",
    "start": 918.457,
    "duration": 0.947
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my God.",
    "start": 921.254,
    "duration": 1.06
  },
  {
    "text": "This is flaming butane rocket on 3, 2, 1.",
    "start": 923.174,
    "duration": 14.815
  },
  {
    "text": "My God.",
    "start": 937.989,
    "duration": 0.699
  },
  {
    "text": "Where did it go?",
    "start": 938.77,
    "duration": 1.284
  },
  {
    "text": "How do you feel?",
    "start": 940.104,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "That was scary!",
    "start": 941.13,
    "duration": 0.959
  },
  {
    "text": "Science rocks!",
    "start": 942.089,
    "duration": 0.766
  },
  {
    "text": "Guys.",
    "start": 942.855,
    "duration": 0.274
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's keep this going.",
    "start": 943.211,
    "duration": 1.123
  },
  {
    "text": "If you want to watch $1\nversus $100,000 yoyo,",
    "start": 944.416,
    "duration": 2.414
  },
  {
    "text": "click here to watch that video.",
    "start": 946.912,
    "duration": 1.637
  },
  {
    "text": "And click here to watch a video\nthat YouTube thinks you'll love.",
    "start": 948.631,
    "duration": 3.463
  }
]